<% front_end_url = ENV.fetch("FRONTEND_URL", "http://localhost:5173") %>
<p>Hello <%= @resource.first_name.presence || @resource.email %>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your Page Chat account.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= "#{front_end_url}/reset-password?token=#{@token}&email=#{ERB::Util.url_encode(@resource.email)}" %>">
    Click here to set a new password
  </a>
</p>

<p>If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email and your password will stay the same.</p>

<p>— The Page Chat Team</p>

